# .env.example — local, non-secret template for the agent-delivery-harness.
#
# This is the ONE shared local-config mechanism. Copy it to .env and fill in
# real values. .env is gitignored; this template is committed and must NEVER
# contain a real secret (connection string, key, or password).
#
# Nothing auto-sources this file. Add project-local, non-secret settings here
# and load them explicitly with `set -a; source .env; set +a`.
